data.description: Buyers financing fell through! This gorgeous home is back on the market!!!! Wow!!! What a deal! Seller needs to sell, and has done a pretty nice price improvement!!! Make your appointment to see this gorgeous 2 story home, ready for the next owner! Move in ready!!! Located in one of the areas nicest subdivisions in Deltona, only minutes to I-4, the Orlando Metro Area, the beaches,  Huge contemporary home with 5 bdrms and 4 full bths. Includes a huge eat in and tiled gourmet  kitchen with granite countertops and a long breakfast bar overlooking the large family room that also leads to the rear covered porch and backyard. Downstairs you will also find a spacious formal dining and living rooms and a bedroom and full bath. Upstairs you will find 4 more big bedrooms and 3 full baths including the massive master suite with a walk-in closet as big as most bedrooms and includes the master bath with a garden tub and separate shower. Also upstairs you have a huge bonus room perfect to be used for an office/Den/media room, etc... 3 car garage, fenced in, and mature landscaping. Call today and schedule your tour! Available on the weekend!
